<tr id="L5"><td><a href="#L5">5</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Configuration unidentified. Ion propulsion, high velocity, though of a unique technology.</td></tr>

<tr id="L6"><td><a href="#L6">6</a></td><td>KIRK:  Any contact, Lieutenant?</td></tr>

<tr id="L7"><td><a href="#L7">7</a></td><td>UHURA:  Hailing on all frequencies, sir. All languages have been attempted. No response. Now using standard interstellar symbols.</td></tr>

<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>KIRK:  Keep trying.</td></tr>

