<tr id="L22"><td><a href="#L22">22</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: A woman materialises and smiles at them.</td></tr>

<tr id="L23"><td><a href="#L23">23</a></td><td>KIRK:  I'm Captain James Kirk. This is the Starship Enterprise.</td></tr>

<tr id="L24"><td><a href="#L24">24</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The security guards rush in, she presses a button on her wrist band, the power goes off and everyone collapses. Then the same happens to the crew all over the ship. The woman walks over to Spock, and puts her hand on his head.</td></tr>

<tr id="L25"><td><a href="#L25">25</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Later - after the opening titles - the power comes back on and everyone wakes up again.</td></tr>

