<tr id="L153"><td><a href="#L153">153</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The group of bearded, skin clad males with clubs move carefully towards the Starfleet party.</td></tr>

<tr id="L154"><td><a href="#L154">154</a></td><td>KIRK:  Fire only on my signal. Flank out.</td></tr>

<tr id="L155"><td><a href="#L155">155</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The primitives suddenly leap up from behind rocks, throwing stones and their clubs. Kirk fires, and stuns the leader. The rest run away.</td></tr>

<tr id="L156"><td><a href="#L156">156</a></td><td>KIRK:  We mean you no harm. We're not your enemies, we're your friends. We only wish to talk to you.</td></tr>

<tr id="L157"><td><a href="#L157">157</a></td><td>MORG:  You are not the Others?</td></tr>

<tr id="L158"><td><a href="#L158">158</a></td><td>KIRK:  No. We come from a far place. We are men.</td></tr>

<tr id="L159"><td><a href="#L159">159</a></td><td>MORG:  Men?</td></tr>

